<abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract:">John P. MacDonald was the Director of the University of Connecticut Libraries from 1963 through 1986.  The collection contains correspondence, reports, studies and information on the Libraries' and associated programs, as well as materials pertaining to MacDonald's interests in birds.</abstract>


</did>


